  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      464.83,
      542.62,
      477.79
    ],
    "text": "The instant application for revision has been filled to set aside the order dated",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      488.71,
      542.72,
      501.67
    ],
    "text": "27.08.2021 of the high Court of Gampaha. The accused in this matter namely",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      512.47,
      542.67,
      525.43
    ],
    "text": "AlahakoonArachchilageNamalNishantha has been indicted in the High Court for",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      536.23,
      542.65,
      549.19
    ],
    "text": "possession and trafficking of 8.5 grams of Heroin. The accused had been arrested in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      560.11,
      542.67,
      573.07
    ],
    "text": "19.07.2019. Indictment has been forwarded on 28.04.2021. The trial is to be taken up",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      583.87,
      542.66,
      596.83
    ],
    "text": "on the 08.04.2022. The main grievance of the petitioner is that, there is a delay of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      607.78,
      479.67,
      620.74
    ],
    "text": "filing the indictment even upon receipt of the government analyst report.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      643.54,
      542.64,
      656.5
    ],
    "text": "But this Court notes that the Attorney General has taken steps to file the indictment",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      85.58,
      667.3,
      539.91,
      680.26
    ],
    "text": "within 1 year and 9 months inspite of the COVID pandemic starting from March 2019.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      728.23,
      323.33,
      756.04
    ],
    "text": "Page 3 of 4",
    "fonts": [
      "BookmanOldStyle",
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      9.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      74.64,
      529.21,
      87.6
    ],
    "text": "According to the provisions of the Poisons, Opium and Dangerous Drugs Act No. 13 of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      98.42,
      529.05,
      111.38
    ],
    "text": "1984, if a suspect is indicted under the same, he or she can be enlarged on bail only",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      122.3,
      529.03,
      135.26
    ],
    "text": "upon exceptional circumstances. The term exceptional has not been defined in the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      146.06,
      521.67,
      159.02
    ],
    "text": "Act. But several decided cases has defined many factors to be exceptional which are",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      167.81,
      529.12,
      237.62
    ],
    "text": "1) The nature of the accusation 2) The culpability of the accused 3) The severity of the sentence if convicted 4) The health condition of the accused or suspect which would be aggravated by",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      242.9,
      201.31,
      255.86
    ],
    "text": "the incarceration",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      273.17,
      529.07,
      286.13
    ],
    "text": "Hence up to now, what has evolved is that the exceptionality would be decided by",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      296.93,
      529.59,
      309.89
    ],
    "text": "the facts of each case, but in the case of Cader v OIC narcotics Bureau 2006 3 SLR 74",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      320.81,
      529.27,
      333.77
    ],
    "text": "Eric Basnayake J said that, these types of offences affect the society at large and",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      344.57,
      526.55,
      357.53
    ],
    "text": "the law should not be made impotent that it does not serve the society and the anti-",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      368.33,
      529.53,
      381.29
    ],
    "text": "social elements should not be given license to create havoc in the society citing the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      392.21,
      472.95,
      405.17
    ],
    "text": "case of Abdul Hamidkari Path and etc v State of Gujarat and other 15 476.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      427.99,
      529.18,
      440.95
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, the law pertaining to the instant matter has provided for the accused",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      451.75,
      529.07,
      464.71
    ],
    "text": "person to be remanded until the conclusion of the trial if not for exceptional",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      475.63,
      529.06,
      488.59
    ],
    "text": "circumstances. In the instant matter, the exceptionality pleaded is the delay in filing",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      499.39,
      509.07,
      512.35
    ],
    "text": "the indictment. The term delay has been considered by this Court in several cases.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      535.15,
      529.45,
      548.11
    ],
    "text": "In the case of Attorney General v Ediriweera (2006) BLR pg. 12, it has been stated",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      559.03,
      528.99,
      571.99
    ],
    "text": "that, delay is always a relative term and the question to be considered is not",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.960000038146973
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
